About me 📱 A strong-willed, supersonic learner & an aspiring Machine Learning Engineer with strengths in communication and innovative thinking. I execute a growth mindset in my work so that I can grasp and adopt new cutting-edge technologies and develop people-centered solutions. My passion projects involve competing at hackathons in DFW metroplex, & attending Society of Women Engineers conferences across the US. This past summer, I volunteered for 48in48 to design & develop a website for a nonprofit organization. Fun fact about me: I’m an absolute nerd for real estate 🏡

UT Dallas x HackReason Hackathon 2022 UT Dallas Building Classifier
